    "info": "Configuracao esperada via variaveis de ambiente:\n\nMQTT_BROKER=192.168.0.10\nNODE_RED_MQTT_BROKER=127.0.0.1\nMQTT_PORT=1883\nNODE_RED_CLIENT_ID=node-red-hand-rehab\n\nComo usar:\n1. Configure o arquivo .env na raiz do repositorio.\n2. Inicie o Node-RED com essas variaveis carregadas.\n3. Importe este fluxo.\n4. Confira o no Broker MQTT Local.\n5. Clique em Deploy.\n\nTopicos:\n- hand-rehab/esp32/status\n- hand-rehab/esp32/mode/set\n- hand-rehab/esp32/mode/state\n- hand-rehab/esp32/buttons\n- hand-rehab/esp32/pressure\n\nPayload de pressao esperado:\n{\"pressure\":0.123,\"pressure_kpa\":0.123,\"pressure_mmhg\":0.92,\"raw\":12345,\"net\":1234,\"timeouts\":0,\"mode\":2}"
